The paper deals with the security and privacy of patients in Telecare medical information systems (TMIS) and proposes an improved two-factor authentication scheme. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Information Theory (cs.IT), Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
